seed_pair.target: I don't care if it's a fast car.
seed_pair.known: No me importa si es un carro rápido.

seed_pair.target: I just want to get there safely.
seed_pair.known: Solo quiero llegar allí con seguridad.

seed_pair.known: No habría podido continuar más tiempo.

seed_pair.target: I wouldn't have been able to without your help.
